      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tokyodorm-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 16.5000000954
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_03-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様です……あれ、さくらちゃんに遙子さん\nそれに{user}さんも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good work‚ everyone… Huh? Sakura-chan‚ Haruko-san?\nAnd Manager-san?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_03-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "揃いも揃って難しい顔をして……どうしたんですの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What’s with all the long faces?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.7333334287,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_03-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "あ、みんな\nえっと、今どりきゅんが生配信をしてて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ hey everyone.\nUm… DoriKyun’s doing a live stream right now…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_03-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "次の対戦相手を指名するって言ってるのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They said they’re gonna nominate their next opponent.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.1527185281,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "事務所を通さないで発言したところで\n意味はないと思うんだが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It doesn’t really matter who they call out\nif they’re not going through the office…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_03-ngs005.m4a",
      "text": "私達にも見せてもらっていい？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Can we watch it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.5238181432,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
