    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_big4-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 51.1722080549
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "lmn",
      "speakerName": "大須賀れもん",
      "speakerNameEn": "Lemon",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-lmn.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_03-lmn001.m4a",
      "text": "それで、次の対戦相手なんだけど……\nん～、どうしようかな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ about our next opponent…\nHmm~ what should we do?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.7233438934,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s3",
      "startTime": 60.1372938077
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "lim",
      "speakerName": "小南来夢",
      "speakerNameEn": "Laim",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-lim.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_03-lim001.m4a",
      "text": "おーおー、コメントが山ほどきてんな\nでも、お前らが挙げたヤツはみーんな逃げたぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Whoa whoa‚ there’s a mountain of comments.\nBut all the ones you guys brought up ran away.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s3",
      "startTime": 69.3500254791
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "lim",
      "speakerName": "小南来夢",
      "speakerNameEn": "Laim",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-lim.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_03-lim002.m4a",
      "text": "あ、そうだ。れもん、あいつらとかいいんじゃねぇか？\n四人になった――月のテンペスト",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ right. Lemon‚ how about those guys?\nThe ones who became a four-member group - Moon Tempest.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.2000030518,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_way_noon",
      "startTime": 78.9965219895
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_trouble-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 79.2631158034
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "Everyone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "え……っ！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh…!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.0631853501,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_03-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "ど、どういうことですの！？\n彼女達とはこの間戦ったばかりですわよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wh-what does this mean!?\nWe just fought them the other day!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.400005595,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_03-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "あれだけ圧倒的に打ち負かしておいて……\n意図が見えませんね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We defeated them so overwhelmingly…\nI don’t get what they’re trying to do.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.9333389283,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s3",
      "startTime": 94.9941343069
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s3",
      "startTime": 94.9941343069
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "lmn",
      "speakerName": "大須賀れもん",
      "speakerNameEn": "Lemon",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-lmn.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_03-lmn002.m4a",
      "text": "月ストね、いいんじゃない？\nあらら、チャットが凄い速さで流れてる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Moon Tempest‚ huh? Sounds good.\nOh my‚ the chat’s scrolling by so fast.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.4084509607,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "lmn",
      "speakerName": "大須賀れもん",
      "speakerNameEn": "Lemon",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-lmn.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_03-lmn003.m4a",
      "text": "「え！？」とか「意外」とか\nみんな理由を知りたがってるみたいだけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "“Huh!?” and “Unexpected‚” huh?\nSeems like everyone wants to know the reason.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s3",
      "startTime": 108.5702953498
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "lim",
      "speakerName": "小南来夢",
      "speakerNameEn": "Laim",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-lim.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_03-lim003.m4a",
      "text": "あたしら、復帰して早々、ライブバトルで\nアイドルどもを潰し過ぎたんだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Right after we made our comeback‚ we crushed\na ton of idols in live battles.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.7666687012,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s3",
      "startTime": 114.4714749734
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "lmn",
      "speakerName": "大須賀れもん",
      "speakerNameEn": "Lemon",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-lmn.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_03-lmn004.m4a",
      "text": "BIG4チャレンジも、美味しいチャンスだって\n飛びついてきたアイドルが初めは結構いたんだけどね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There were actually a lot of idols who jumped\nat the chance to participate in the BIG4 challenge at first.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.3666687012,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s3",
      "startTime": 121.8079678218
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "lim",
      "speakerName": "小南来夢",
      "speakerNameEn": "Laim",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-lim.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_03-lim004.m4a",
      "text": "負けてアイドルを辞めたヤツが増えてきて、そのうち\nビビって誰も挑んでこなくなったんだよな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The number of idols who quit after losing kept increasing‚\nand then no one dared to challenge us anymore out of fear.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.3666687012,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_rival-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 128.7666676839
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s3",
      "startTime": 129.0990023534
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "lim",
      "speakerName": "小南来夢",
      "speakerNameEn": "Laim",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-lim.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_03-lim005.m4a",
      "text": "全く話になんねぇ。ぼろ負けして折れる程度の\n覚悟でアイドルやってんじゃねぇよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This is ridiculous. Don’t call yourself an idol\nif you’re just gonna break after losing badly.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.3333353679,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s3",
      "startTime": 136.3883069198
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "lmn",
      "speakerName": "大須賀れもん",
      "speakerNameEn": "Lemon",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-lmn.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_03-lmn005.m4a",
      "text": "でも、一度私達に惨敗して、その上メンバーが\n一人欠けても続けてるグループがいる……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But there’s this one group who continued on\neven after being utterly defeated by us and losing a member…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.3333353679,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s3",
      "startTime": 144.3484655778
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "lim",
      "speakerName": "小南来夢",
      "speakerNameEn": "Laim",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-lim.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_03/sud_vo_adv_main_03_08_03-lim006.m4a",
      "text": "今のお前らの力はどうなんだ？\n暇潰しに相手してやるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "How strong are you right now?\nI’ll play with you to kill some time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148.066668876,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "lim",
      "speakerName": "小南来夢",
      "speakerNameEn": "Laim",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-lim.png",
